OL,3,CMoment police find driver asleep in
OL,4,Ccar during drink drive crackdown
OL,6,FFootage has been released of the
OL,7,Fmoment a driver is found asleep behind
OL,8,Fthe wheel while his engine was running
OL,9,Fin Hove.
OL,11,FBlake Densley was arrested by police
OL,12,Fwho were alerted to a man asleep in a
OL,13,Fvehicle on Hangleton Way on 17
OL,14,FDecember during a Christmas drink and
OL,15,Fdrug drive crackdown by Sussex Police.
OL,17,FThe scaffolder was charged with
OL,18,Ffailing to provide a specimen of
OL,19,Fbreath for analysis and failing to co-
OL,20,Foperate with a preliminary test.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
