OL,3,CMoment police find driver asleep in
OL,4,Ccar during drink drive crackdown
OL,6,FHe was disqualified from driving for
OL,7,F12 months, and fined #750, and ordered
OL,8,Fto pay #85 costs a #300 victim
OL,9,Fsurcharge.
OL,11,FHe's one of 279 people who were
OL,12,Farrested during the operation, which
OL,13,Fran from 1 December to 1 January.
OL,15,FOf these, so far 80 have been
OL,16,Fconvicted.
OL,18,FCharlie Palmer, 33, an electrician, of
OL,19,FChurch Close, Shipley, was
OL,20,Fdisqualified from driving for 36
OL,21,Fmonths.
