OL,3,CMoment police find driver asleep in
OL,4,Ccar during drink drive crackdown
OL,6,FKrystle Jones, 40, a travel industry
OL,7,Femployee, of Collingwood Close,
OL,8,FPeacehaven, was arrested in Brighton
OL,9,FRoad, Newhaven, on 27 December.
OL,11,FShe was disqualified from driving for
OL,12,F12 months, and fined #100, and ordered
OL,13,Fto pay #85 costs a #40 victim
OL,14,Fsurcharge.
OL,16,FVanessa Jones, 53, unemployed, of
OL,17,FMaesycoed Road, Rhondda Cynon Taf,
OL,18,FWales, was arrested in Perimeter Road
OL,19,FNorth, Crawley, on 29 December.
